casebody.data:
No. 918. Great Lakes Airlines, Inc., et al. v. Civil Aeronautics Board. Thurman Arnold, Charles H. Older and Albert F. Beitel for petitioners. Solicitor General Cox, Assistant Attorney General Loevinger, Bichard A. Solomon, Bobert A. Hammond III, Joseph B. Goldman, O. D. Ozment and Bobert L. Toomey for respondent.

Reported below: _ U. S. App. D. C. _, _ F. 2d _.

United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Douglas is of the opinion that certiorari should be granted. Mr. Justice Brennan took no part in the consideration or decision of this application.
